    <mxCell id="11" value="Oxford Pets / Stanford Cars / CUB-200
~14,000 images · 3 classes
224×224 RGB" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="173" y="118" width="419" height="84" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="12" value="DINO ViT-S/8  (frozen + optional fine-tune)

Multi-layer extraction: L8 + L10 + L12
→ concat → 1,152-dim patch vector

FG attention masking: top 40% patches kept
(CLS token attention as foreground detector)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="173" y="228" width="419" height="114" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="13" value="GMM  (30 clusters)

PCA: 1,152 → 128 dim  (≈90% variance)
Spatial features appended (row/col position)
Spatial smoothing: majority-vote cleanup" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="173" y="368" width="419" height="84" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="14" value="Human SME inspects patch cluster grids
→ assigns semantic label per cluster
   e.g.  &quot;cat_ear&quot;  |  &quot;wheel_rim&quot;  |  &quot;wing_tip&quot;

Stored in  cache/labels.json" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="173" y="478" width="419" height="99" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="15" value="Concept activation scores → LogReg
Predicts: Cat / Car / Bird
3-panel explanation figure per image
(original | concept map | contribution bar)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="173" y="603" width="419" height="74" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="16" value="NHANES 2013–2018  ·  18,673 records
34 lab tests across 3 clinical panels:
CBC (14 tests) · BMP (17 tests) · Lipid (4 tests)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="623" y="118" width="419" height="84" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="17" value="PanelFTTransformer  (PSFTT — novel)

Per-feature tokenizer: T_i = x_i·W_i + b_i
Panel positional encoding (CBC / BMP / Lipid)

Two-scale SSL pre-training:
  · Within-panel masking (40% per panel)
  · Cross-panel dropout (whole-panel dropout)

Multi-layer: L2 + L4 + L6 → 384-dim panel-patch" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="623" y="228" width="419" height="114" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="18" value="Per-panel GMM  (3 panels × 10 clusters = 30)

PCA: 34 → 20 dim
Panel-patch features [N × 3 × 384]
Separate clusterer per clinical panel" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="623" y="368" width="419" height="84" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="19" value="LLM reads deviation profile of cluster centroid
→ suggests clinical concept label + differentials
→ Human clinician validates / corrects
   e.g.  &quot;CBC anaemia pattern&quot;  |  &quot;Metabolic syndrome&quot;

Stored in  cache/lab/labels.json" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="623" y="478" width="419" height="99" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="20" value="Concept scores → LogReg
Predicts: Diabetes / Hypertension / Normal
